!!!
%html
  %head
    %title Client Mail Panom
    :css
      @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@400;500;700&display=swap');
  %body
    .deviceWidth{:style => "width: 740px;background: #fff;font-family: 'Roboto', Arial, sans-serif; margin:0 auto; padding: 30px 30px 40px;"}
      .deviceWidth{:style => "width: 100%;background: #FFF;font-family: 'Roboto', Arial, sans-serif; margin:0 auto;  border-radius: 45px;"}
        %table{:align => "center", :border => "0", :cellpadding => "0", :cellspacing => "0", :style => "font-family: 'Roboto', Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 28px; background: #fff; border-radius: 45px; border:1px solid #dfdfdf", :width => "100%"}
          %tbody
            %tr
              %td{:colspan => "2", :style => " padding: 0 0;  border-radius: 45px;"}
                %div{:style => "margin:0 auto 50px; padding:0  30px;"}
                  %h1{:style => "font-weight: 500;font-size: 14px;color: #000; margin:0"} Dear #{@lead.name},
                  %span{:style => "font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; color: #000; text-align: left; margin:0 0 10px; line-height: 20px;"}
                    %p
                      Accept Greetings of the day from Panom Developers.
                    %p
                      We are happy to know that you are interested in our project - #{@lead.project.name.upcase} & are looking for further details.
                    %p
                      Spread across 2.5 acres of pristine land with 45+ amenities, PARLESHWAR AANGAN is a one-of-a-kind residential development. To give you a better understanding of the project, we have attached the E-Brochure and a link to the project video - 
                      %a{:href => "https://youtu.be/nImm8ZTbmz4"}
                        https://youtu.be/nImm8ZTbmz4 
                    %p
                      We would be delighted to showcase the development to you personally in our Sales Experience Centre. Our experienced team will be available to answer any questions you may have and provide a comprehensive tour of the property.
                    %p
                      Should you have any queries or require further information, please do not hesitate to reach out to us. You can contact me directly at 7665 831 831 or reply to this email.
                    %p
                      Thank you once again for your interest in #{@lead.project.name.upcase}.
                    %p
                      We are excited about the opportunity to assist you in finding your dream home at #{@lead.project.name.upcase}.
                    %p
                      Warm Regards,
                      %br
                      Seemeen Lakdawala
                      %br
                      Manager - PreSales
                      %br
                      7665 831 831
                      %br
                      Panom Developers
                      %br
                      www.panomdevelopers.com
